{"tid":2122474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免費武肺檢查係林奠幫中共嘅回血劍","createTime":"2020-07-24T04:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T12:45:25.000Z","uid":47614,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f78bc84121ac837a2078c9d6f2de2f039e427c","tid":2122474,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"仆街奠月娥上星期低調咁宣佈咗，仲要一星期後極速推行。以我所知都已經有好多安老院、殘院等等同事開始做緊/做咗。呢樣嘢仲仆街過佢啲垃圾抗疫政府，就係「送中」。<br />\n<br />\n「政府以直接採購服務方式，<span class=\"red\">向華昇診斷中心、中國檢驗有限公司及Prenetics</span>三家檢測中心採購檢測服務，為院舍員工......進行病毒檢測，涉及人數約四十萬。」<br />\n三間私人企業，其中一間唔使講，講下其他兩間。<br />\n<br />\n首先，華昇診斷中心：據公司註冊處，華昇於上月9日成立，創辦成員包括<span class=\"red\">華大基因健康科技（香港）有限公司</span>，持四成股份；登記地址位於大埔工業邨，<span class=\"red\">由深圳華大基因股份有限公司全資持有</span>。董事長係<span class=\"red\">胡定旭</span>，佢係醫管局前主席、<span class=\"red\">現任全國政協常委</span>。最仆街嘅係，呢間華大最近係俾美國制裁，原因係<span class=\"red\">涉嫌協助採集與分析維吾爾族嘅DNA</span>。（詳見：<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1595291278092&amp;issue=20200721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1595291278092%26issue%3D20200721&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6FEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=81e79627\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1595291278092&amp;issue=20200721</a>）<br />\n<br />\n另一間，Prenetics：google完佢嗰page好似好信得過，全部英文咁。錯。Prenetics公司旗下嘅檢測Project &quot;Project Screen by Circle&quot; 係由<span class=\"red\">Circle DNA</span>去做。而Circle DNA係由<span class=\"red\">貝瑞基因</span>同Prenetics共同投資創立，貝瑞基因係<span class=\"red\">中國嘅臨床基因組學檢測公司</span>。<br />\n<br />\n結論：免費嘅嘢係最貴。<br />\n仆街正苦仲要唔公開招標，明明有資源去加大本地檢測率，點解仲要搵其他公司？除咗利益輸送去救中共國企，仲要係出賣你獨有嘅DNA資料。<br />\n勸大家唔好因為老細叫到就去做，更加唔好因為免費去做。寧願你俾多幾百蚊去診所做仲好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">有冇社福界工會可以跟進下</span><br />\n<br />\n仆街林奠之前推lump sum grant<br />\n而家又靠社福界幫中共回血"},{"pid":"f4d7d0b97144beed996f7e8166e31bf7efb54ea6","tid":2122474,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643970f443cc5ff70cdf4669ad4146501effea7d","tid":2122474,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac83855ac417679c08eb53bdb37ddbd2e9c8a00","tid":2122474,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77658e307726020fddc026fc8a73e11aabce9fff","tid":2122474,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63606d3d937447ce933b439c9e1c984b024f40df","tid":2122474,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62149924d7d3eddc136473f8364f4314797437e","tid":2122474,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"我做物管pt<br />\n但公司唔撚叫我申請抗疫基金 物管前線<br />\n正係叫我輸送dna<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3d407a84dff4587a2ae41fc0e097e1e1de2dac","tid":2122474,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726b2510787859180332a23a802ef0fbdd65a77c","tid":2122474,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f6b98adad1031d6369a886fc6e500fae213b5a","tid":2122474,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:43:39.000Z","msg":"點回都冇用，淨係識回血唔識攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比人磨死係遲早問題，敵人仲要下下爆擊"},{"pid":"e7c5d6beea792fba12344f43670eaec090ba7677","tid":2122474,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}